#videos
  %h1.responsive-body Video library
  Some of these videos appear in the CS Principles programming unit and are displayed here as a quick introduction to each of the main concepts from the unit. Check out each video to see how you can add new features to your app.
  - DB[:cdo_cspunit3_videos].each do |item|
    // Show the chapter title at the 
    // beginning of each video chapter
    - unless item[:category_title_s].nil_or_empty?
      .clear
      %h2= item[:category_title_s]
    %div{style: "float:left; padding:10px; width: 275px;"}
      = view :display_video_thumbnail, id: item[:id_s],  video_code:item[:code_s], caption: item[:caption_s], play_button: 'center', download_path: item[:download_path_s]
      - unless item[:studio_stage_s].nil_or_empty?
        %a{href: CDO.studio_url(item[:studio_stage_s])} Try it now

:javascript
  $(function() {
    $('.highlight-item').mouseover(function() {
      var caption = $(this).find('.highlight-caption');
      caption.fadeIn();
    });

    $('.highlight-item').mouseleave(function() {
      var caption = $(this).find('.highlight-caption');
      caption.fadeOut();
    });
  });
